      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "spherical harmonic",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[\"Y\"_l^m(vartheta, varphi) = [((2l+1)/(4pi)) ((l-abs m)!)/((l+ abs m)!)\\]^(1//2) P_l^(abs m) (\"cos\" vartheta)\"e\"^(\"i\" m varphi)]\n\n(for stem:[l, abs(m) in bb(sf(N)); abs(m) <= l])\n\nSolution of\n\nstem:[1/(\"sin \"vartheta) del/(del vartheta) (sin vartheta (del y)/(del vartheta)) + 1/(\"sin\"^2 vartheta) (del^2y)/(del varphi^2) + l(l+1)y=0]\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-2-20"
